fields.title: Spectacular VR for Nexus 5
fields.description: This is a quick and easy 3D print that turns a Nexus 5 phone into a VR device, inspired by google cardboard. DIY: STL files on Thingiverse 2x M3 bolts and nuts are required, or just use cable ties. 2x 28mm bi-convex lenses (The lenses can be ordered on ebay for a couple of pounds)
